<Layout title="Mission" current="mission">

  <h1>Mission</h1>

  <p style="max-width:760px; line-height:1.7;">
    The Journal of Revised Truth is committed to the disciplined revision of
    what was confidently known yesterday and thoughtfully reconsidered tomorrow.
  </p>

  <p style="max-width:760px; line-height:1.7;">
    We honor those who pursued understanding before it was safe,
    enduring ridicule and, at times, real harm.
  </p>

  <p style="max-width:760px; line-height:1.7;">
    The Journal acknowledges that present conclusions may be revised in light of future understanding.
  </p>

</Layout>